    ('General','About Codee Chatbot','About Codee Chatbot','General','General','General','General','Informational','Hi, I''m Codee! I''m a chatbot designed to help Tech Elevator students get ready for their new careers. I can help you find Pathway presentations, ask interview questions, or send motivational quotes if you need a little pick-me-up. I can''t wait to chat with you, just type in the bar to get started!','text','n/a','n/a','happy'),
